er users in online multiplayer and take in the sight of the world of Little Witch Academia together! \n\n\n\u00a9 2017 TRIGGER / Yoh Yoshinari / \"Little Witch Academia\" Committee \u00a9 UNIVRS, Inc.", "short_description": "Soar through the skies, hunt for ghosts, and become the best witch racer in the world!\n\n\u00a9 2017 T/YY/LWAC   \u00a9 UNIV"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Squere_JP_202012.png", "id": "1327244154279833", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982648_1327244157613166_2961322866020914640_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=i5lnKq_C1owQ7kNvgGzdA-P&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAAfoYTTgjIAzAsRxpEe0xUMAEkvTCfnDlPvfeMSUmy1w&oe=6740838E"}, {"file_name": "mini_JP_202012.png", "id": "767739813819324", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974453_767739817152657_5763260574459999295_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=DQeZEeRYfnsQ7kNvgEvQpVk&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBp6dd21W6C4LjZFJ8iVTSr_DmiK6-_C6S9crXH0ePrIQ&oe=67406E66"}, {"file_name": "Portrait_JP_202012.png", "id": "687368831924916", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974557_687368835258249_3301610840483328822_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=iy5zZEpo1NMQ7kNvgENUQSo&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCdiwIX-CCh5dIZTBLh2TJB-Cg9ZJ-COmMA1JAPUZosWQ&oe=674060B3"}, {"file_name": "Landscape_JP_202012.png", "id": "210773470635130", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39001687_210773473968463_5238021041892551677_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=YGEc3Bopxw8Q7kNvgH9MUnY&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBVdXDm0Gg4zF4sN2ara95J0H1gxCPJMkcaz41KJpp4_w&oe=674070CF"}, {"file_name": "HERO_JP_202012.png", "id